==發行==
=== 評價 ===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]基於115位評論家持有31％的新鮮度，平均得分4.7／10<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/blackhat/ | title=''Blackhat'' | work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] | publisher=[[Flixster|Flixster]] | accessdate=January 20, 2015 | archive-date=2015-01-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150122231229/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/blackhat/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>；[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]根據32條評論，得分49（滿分100）<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/blackhat | title=''Blackhat'' | work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] | publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] | accessdate=January 15, 2015 | archive-date=2015-01-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150123045050/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/blackhat | dead-url=no }}</ref>。整體差評居多，但從事安檢篩選工作的專員們卻很喜歡本片<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.wired.com/2015/01/blackhat-the-best-cyber-movie/ | title=''Is Blackhat the best Cyber movie' | work=[[Wired|Wired]] | accessdate=January 16, 2015 | archive-date=2015-01-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150122092019/http://www.wired.com/2015/01/blackhat-the-best-cyber-movie/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
《黑帽駭客》是一個[[票房炸彈|票房炸彈]]，在首映當天僅獲得了170萬美元的票房<ref name="#1">{{Cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2015/01/blackhat-michael-mann-chris-hemsworth-universal-legendary-box-office-bomb-1201353487/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-01-22 |archive-date=2015-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150122110006/http://deadline.com/2015/01/blackhat-michael-mann-chris-hemsworth-universal-legendary-box-office-bomb-1201353487/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在全球市場上，[[丹麥|丹麥]]、[[希臘|希臘]]、[[波蘭|波蘭]]、[[台灣|台灣]]、[[土耳其|土耳其]]和[[越南|越南]]的票房表現皆不如預期<ref name="#1"/>。

